-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
PLACEHOLDER -- replace with the real step-ca root CA certificate
once platform components (M2 sub-project 2, agentops-platform repo)
issues one. See that sub-project's design doc for the export command.
The build validates this file with openssl x509 and skips it because
it is not a real certificate, so the system CA bundle is left unchanged.
When a real step-ca root replaces this file in place, it is validated
and trusted automatically with no Dockerfile change required.
